<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=68942">My Maglo Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/udldragonbreath.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dldragonbreath</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dubious Poster</span><br> <font color=#778899>(2/4/02 7:13:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1059.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What is *dmg bonus*</span><hr size=1> Depends on which type of bonus you want. If your talking the damage bonus you get as you level and gain skill then if it is 6 your min damage will be 7 bonus + 1. IF it is bane damage such as on the lsoee then that is a random added to the damage so if normally it is 16 and you get a magic checked bain damage when it goes through and it is 5 to magic checked damage it becomes a 21 damage weapon.<br>
